  "summary": [
    "The earth shook. The sea roared. And then...",
    "\r\nThere is a small house solitary standing by the seaside. A pigtail-braided girl has been living there alone since that fateful day. Mail is no longer delivered, but even this morning she's hanging out the laundry as usual. ",
    "\r\nA delicate fable of hope and rebirth in a cruel and gentle world after an unnamed disaster."
